	(8, 2242, '', '', '', '175.223.34.121', '2016-03-20 10:35:56', '2016-03-20 01:35:56', '★ 댓글 작성법★\r\n익명으로 댓글달기를 원하시면 댓글칸(이름, 이메일 불필요)만 입력하시면 됩니다!!', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 4.4.2; IM-A910K Build/KVT49L) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0 Chrome/30.0.0.0 Mobile Safari/537.36;KAKAOTALK 1400223', '', 0, 0),
